version_description:
- Fixed HUD offset for devices with notch
- Tutorial fixes
- Cart income calculation fixes
- Multiple crash fixes

- Stability improvements
- Bug fixes
- UI improvements
- Idle income shows correct values

Greetings Shop Owners! The latest update is now available:
-Save your progress to Facebook, and Game Center!
-Sorting now does a better job of prioritizing your items.
-Improvements have been made to the tutorial.
-Bug fixes and performance optimizations.
Got a cool idea? Email us at support@metamoki.com

Sharpen your swords Shop Keep! The latest update is now available...
-Challenge other Shop Keeps in the open market. Tournaments are now Live!
-The Pretty Princess Event has been added! Everything is pink.
-Change your Name and Avatar in the Settings Menu!
-Various bug fixes.
Need to speak to a manager? Email us at support@metamoki.com
